<http://dx.doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2016.256>
    bibo:endPage "32" ;
    bibo:journal "European Journal of Taxonomy" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2016-12-30" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "256" ;
    dc:creator "Manja Voss; Björn Berning; Erich Reiter" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "A taxonomic and morphological re-evaluation of “ Halitherium ” cristolii Fitzinger, 1842 (Mammalia, Sirenia) from the late Oligocene of Austria, with the description of a new genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889330>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889340>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889332>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889334>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889336>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889338>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889342>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889344>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889346> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889330>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Cranium of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) (OLL 1926 / 394) in dorsal view. A. Photograph. B. Drawing. White areas indicate either missing or reconstructed parts. Scale bar = 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889330/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889340>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Mandibles of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) in right lateral views. A. OLL 2012 / 1 (lectotype). B. OLL 1939 / 257 (holotype of “ Halitherium ” abeli). Outlined areas of the ascending mandibular rami (amr) indicate either missing or reconstructed parts. Scale bar = 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889340/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889332>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Cranium of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) (OLL 1926 / 394) in ventral view. A. Photograph. B. Drawing. White areas indicate either missing or reconstructed parts. Scale bar = 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889332/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889334>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Cranium of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) (OLL 1926 / 394). A. In caudal view. B. In right lateral view. Shaded area indicates either missing or reconstructed part. Scale bars = 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889334/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889336>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Parietal-supraoccipital skullcap of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) (OLL 1899 / 11, holotype of “ Halitherium ” pergense (Toula, 1899 )). A. Drawing in dorsal view. B. Photograph in caudal view. White areas indicate either missing or reconstructed parts. Dashed lines pertain to broken parts. Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889338>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Mandibles of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842). A. Photograph of OLL 1939 / 257 (holotype of “ Halitherium ” abeli (Spillmann, 1959 )) in occlusal view. B. Outline drawing of OLL 2012 / 1 (lectotype) in left lateral view revealing information on the medial side of the right mandible. Dashed lines indicate broken parts. Both outlined (A) and shaded (B) areas indicate either missing or reconstructed parts. Scale bars = 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889342>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. The right upper molars M 1 – M 3 of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) occlusal view. Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889344>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Outline drawings of the left humerus LI 2012 / 4 and the xiphisternum OLL 2012 / 5 of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842). A. Humerus in posterior view. B. Humerus in anterior view. C. Xiphisternum in ventral view. Shaded areas indicate missing parts. Scale bars = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889344/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889346>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Left scapula of Lentiarenium cristolii (Fitzinger, 1842) (OLL 1854 / 327). A. In lateral view. B. In medial view. Scale bar = 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889346/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

